{"tid":1862622,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陳梓維議員選區佐敦南中招了","createTime":"2020-02-04T17:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T13:01:54.000Z","uid":7439,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc83d7dbd60414e4b8c78bcda1d4e39b4dee58d","tid":1862622,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"陳梓維議員辦事處：白加士街柏嘉商業中心1401室<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qySayOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqySayOR.jpg&h=d974c7bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，新增確診的64歲女病人在佐敦恆豐中心LG8開設時裝店「Fresh up」，病人因為插喉未能回答問題，加上時裝店沒有客戶資料，<span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲上月23日到訪過時裝店的市民聯絡衞生防護中心跟進。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200204/s00001/9ddf61d3a78675c2d0bfdbea2c822401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200204%2Fs00001%2F9ddf61d3a78675c2d0bfdbea2c822401.jpg&h=0c9f4610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，女子在佐敦恒豐中心經營一間名為「Fresh Up」的服裝店，舖號為「LG 8」，據悉，店舖在農曆新年初六後曾開門營業；鄰舖一名姓張女職員稱，該店舖在上址開業10多年，商場內職員大多互相認識，染病女子年約60多歲，與弟婦一同經營，<span style=\"color: red;\">售賣日本時裝及孕婦服式等</span>，初六自己沒有上班，但得悉染病女子回來開舖，精神欠佳，覺得她不舒服，至今日政府公佈才知她是確診肺炎病毒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3954600/org/ce5cd2d01fdf038fb665a1cf0a3855da.JPG/_z2Lg6m15xgadd_kQ32Ea-IsnOxbRDaSHWq-2Ddqvtg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3954600%2Forg%2Fce5cd2d01fdf038fb665a1cf0a3855da.JPG%2F_z2Lg6m15xgadd_kQ32Ea-IsnOxbRDaSHWq-2Ddqvtg&h=c033adf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張小姐另一角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d532cdde3508413b11fc9a275e4252a8637ada80","tid":1862622,"uid":7439,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"陳梓維手下敗將葉傲冬返咗文匯報做助理總編輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83635cffdf9d73930c41fd7a8e339e952c235495","tid":1862622,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"